title: Segmentation fault when running ignition gazebo blueprint

content.raw:
**Expected behavior:**  
Was following the tutorial written [here](https://ignitionrobotics.org/docs/blueprint/ros_integration)

However ignition gazebo segfaults when running

```
ign gazebo -r camera_sensor.sdf
```
